de:

en: Decision No. 1/2024 of the Joint Switzerland-United Kingdom committee on Agriculture on modification of Annex 9 to the Incorporated Agriculture Agreement - 17-12-2024 - Trade Agreement between the Swiss Confederation and the United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland
